**/.env.*.local

# Build artifacts and logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# Fastlane (If used for deployments)
**/fastlane/report.xml
**/fastlane/Preview.html

# System Files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

